passages.text:
Oh thank god. You have no idea how long I've been waiting for you.
[[Do I know you?|Know you]]
passages.name: Start

passages.text:
No, we're strangers. But that's exactly why I'm so excited to see you! I came here about a month ago in order to conduct research for a book about harvest celebrations, but I can't get anyone in this entire town to talk to me for more than thirty seconds.
[[Continue]]
passages.name: Know you

passages.text:
I feel like I'm getting cabin fever. All anyone wants to talk about on this tiny island is their precious festival, but I can never get anyone to give me any details on any of their customs or rituals. Do you think you could help me out a bit?
[[Sure!|sure]]
[[No thanks, I don't want to get involved.|No involved]]

links.name: No thanks, I don't want to get involved.|No involved
links.link: No thanks, I don't want to get involved.|No involved

passages.name: Continue

passages.text:
Ah, wonderful! Thank you! Just let me know if you discover anything noteworthy. I have a feeling that there has to be at least one interesting thing to learn from these people. Otherwise I'll have made this trip for nothing...
[[I'll let you know if I find anything|Bye]]

links.name: I'll let you know if I find anything|Bye
links.link: I'll let you know if I find anything|Bye

passages.name: sure

passages.text:
No? Well, it's up to you, but if you want my opinion, it seems near impossible to stay uninvolved in this town. For what little information these people offer up about themselves, they've sure seemed interested in me since I arrived...
[[Cointinue2]]
passages.name: No involved

passages.text:
Let me know if you change your mind. I'm sure there's at least one interesting thing to learn from these people. Otherwise I'll have made this trip for nothing...
[[I'll see you around.|Bye]]
passages.name: Cointinue2
